<plot>A cannon awakens the players and they hustle off to the nearest bond booth. They whiz through the air, bowling over pedestrians. Ben takes the American flag away from a citizen who is not buying bonds and takes him away. The scene changes to the Kaiser's dugout in Berlin, where the German flag is lowered, and the Stars and Stripes is raised in its place.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?270504</url></doc>
